                <div class="col-xl-4 d-flex align-items-stretch">
                  <div class="icon-box mt-4 mt-xl-0">
                    <i class="ri-building-line"></i>
                    <h4>OUR SCHOOL</h4>
                    <p>Established in 1872, as innovators of international education in Japan,continues to meet the needs of children (co-educational, 2½ years to Grade 12) from the multi-cultural, multi-faith international community.
</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 d-flex align-items-stretch">
                  <div class="icon-box mt-4 mt-xl-0">
                    <i class="ri-community-fill"></i>
                    <h4>COMMUNITY</h4>
                    <p>Our school is dedicated not only to cater to the learning and developmental needs of its students across grade levels, but to also be a support and a driving force for its extended community of neighbors, families, and alumni.
</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 d-flex align-items-stretch">
                  <div class="icon-box mt-4 mt-xl-0">
                    <i class="ri-book-read-line"></i>
                    <h4>LEARNING</h4>
                    <p>The Saint Maur Essential Outcomes (SMEOs) represent the dispositions we hope to instill in each of our students. Members of the school community will seek to live as moral citizens, unique individuals, global citizens, balanced and life-long learners.
</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div><!-- End .content-->
